foods.description: WOOD FRIED ITALIAN CRUST PIZZA, 5 MUSHROOM MEDLEY
foods.lowercaseDescription: wood fried italian crust pizza, 5 mushroom medley
foods.ingredients: CRUST: SOFT WHEAT FLOUR, WATER, EXTRA VIRGIN OLIVE OIL, SUNFLOWER OIL, SALT, YEAST. CHEESE: LOW MOISTURE MOZZARELLA CHEESE (PASTEURIZED MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SALT, ENZYMES), FONTINA CHEESE (PASTEURIZED MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SALT, ENZYMES). SAUCE: WATER, CREAMY ROASTED GARLIC SAUCE (WHOLE MILK POWDER, BUTTERMILK SOLIDS [WHEY SOLIDS, BUTTERMILK, DRIED CREAM], MODIFIED FOOD STARCH [CORN], GARLIC POWDER, SALT, MALTODEXTRIN, SOY LECITHIN, XANTHAN GUM, SPICE, CANOLA OIL, NATURAL FLAVORS, CONTAINS LESS THAN 2% CALCIUM SILICATE AND SILICON DIOXIDE [ANTI-CAKING AGENTS]), OLIVE OIL. MUSHROOM BLEND: WHITE MUSHROOMS, PORTABELLA MUSHROOMS, CRIMINI MUSHROOMS, SHIITAKE MUSHROOMS, PORCINI MUSHROOMS. CARAMELIZED ONIONS: ONION, NATURAL ONION FLAVORING. ROASTED RED PEPPERS. GARNISH: DEHYDRATED GARLIC, DEHYDRATE RED BELL PEPPER, SPICES. THYME.
foods.allHighlightFields: Ingredients: LESS THAN 2% CALCIUM SILICATE AND SILICON DIOXIDE [ANTI-CAKING AGENTS]), OLIVE OIL. MUSHROOM BLEND
